title: Did the company call GOP'sad' and'stoppid' to criticize it?
subtitle: The Republicans criticized the high prices on clothes worn by the U.S. Republic of Alexandria Okasio Cortez at a photo shoot in Vanity Fair.
author: Nur Ibrahim
vclaim: ==History==Alexandria Okasio Cortez of the United States called Republicans "Sad" and "Stupid" after conservatives criticized her for wearing a $14,000 cost cost cost cost cost cost cost cost cost cost cost cost cost for a story at the Vanity Festival in December 2020.
